tip.text: The Homestyle Cock-a-doodle soup has a thicker consistency compared to the light clear broth at Raffles City. However, no complaints. Order the set meal and try the Tandoori wrap!
I enjoyed the Homestyle Cock-a-Doodle soup, it's a light clear broth w/ generous chunks of tender chicken, diced carrots, celery and flat noodles. Perfect!
